00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#f5f0ef">I'll be fine!</font></b></font></font>

151
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#f6f5f3">I'll be fine!</font></b></font></font>

152
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like Mom can handle 
the inn by herself.</font>

153
00:08:19,740 --> 00:08:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She can?</font>

154
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! That's close!</font>

155
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What? What is that sound?</font>

156
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That lightning strike might have 
knocked something over in the back.</font>

157
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

158
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go check the back entrance!</font>

159
00:08:45,300 --> 00:08:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

160
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for lending me something to wear.</font>

161
00:10:18,450 --> 00:10:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

162
00:10:19,780 --> 00:10:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are the only things 
I had here in your size.</font>

163
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bought that track jacket 
to practice cleaning stains on.</font>

164
00:10:27,110 --> 00:10:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is totally fine with me. 
Thanks a lot.</font>

165
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't offer much, but why 
don't you eat before you go?</font>

166
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

167
00:10:35,030 --> 00:10:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, but I really don't want to impose.</font>

168
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's no trouble at all.</font>

169
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think of it as thanks for putting 
the washing machine back upright.</font>

170
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

171
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

172
00:11:03,930 --> 00:11:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really do appreciate the help. 
Thank you so much.</font>

173
00:11:08,310 --> 00:11:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's nothing I could've 
done about it by myself.</font>

174
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

175
00:11:26,710 --> 00:11:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yum! This dried fish...</font>

176
00:11:29,130 --> 00:11:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It tastes the same as the fish 
we serve guests at the inn.</font>

177
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, isn't it good?</font>

178
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from that store by the beach,</font>

179
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#b7c0ce">Gift Shop</font></b></font>

180
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#c2ccdc"><font size="17">Atsuei Dried Fish Shop</font></font></b></font>

181
00:11:36,090 --> 00:11:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Atsuei Dried Fish Shop.</font>

182
00:11:36,090 --> 00:11:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Atsuei Dried Fish Shop.</font>

183
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first time I tasted it, 
I was so impressed.</font>

184
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go, honey. Enjoy.</font>

185
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? But I'm still 
on the clock right now.</font>

