204
00:12:37,230 --> 00:12:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? Call?</i></font>

205
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello?</font>

206
00:12:44,250 --> 00:12:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

207
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, we're fine.</font>

208
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And over there?</font>

209
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's good.</font>

210
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You want me to put Kinme-san on?</font>

211
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom says she wants to talk.</font>

212
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? To me?</font>

213
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Ishimochi-san? Good evening.</font>

214
00:13:04,630 --> 00:13:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh... No, it's no trouble.</font>

215
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not at all. In fact, 
I should be the one apologizing.</font>

216
00:13:12,710 --> 00:13:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, I see.</font>

217
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm real sorry about this, Kinme-san.</font>

218
00:13:17,690 --> 00:13:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can drive over and pick Kyu up. 
It'll probably be pretty late, though.</font>

219
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too dangerous, Ishimochi-san.</font>

220
00:13:24,690 --> 00:13:27,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't go outside,
even if it is in a car.</font>

221
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rain and winds are too strong, 
and we have no idea when it will stop.</font>

222
00:13:31,650 --> 00:13:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know, but I've got to 
pick him up sooner or later.</i></font>

223
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, maybe I'll just...</font>

224
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have Kyusho-kun spend the night here.</font>

225
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

226
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's perfectly fine! 
Please don't worry about it.</font>

227
00:13:46,970 --> 00:13:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Goodbye.</font>

228
00:13:48,790 --> 00:13:50,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, I really shouldn't...</font>

229
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine! Don't worry about it.</font>

230
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

231
00:13:58,730 --> 00:14:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really okay! No need to worry.</font>

232
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll set it up so we can sleep 
in separate rooms.</font>

233
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The second floor storage room 
is empty right now, anyway.</font>

234
00:14:08,740 --> 00:14:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

235
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you've already done so much...</font>

236
00:14:15,250 --> 00:14:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got everything covered. Let's just 
say the feeling is mutual, so it's fine.</font>

237
00:14:21,370 --> 00:14:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't depend on Kyusho-kun all the time.</i></font>

238
00:14:24,020 --> 00:14:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I gotta show him I'm dependable too!</i></font>

239
00:14:26,890 --> 00:14:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

240
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I wonder why the power 
hasn't come back yet.</font>

241
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's been a while.</font>

242
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't feel great about leaving 
that unfinished laundry overnight.</i></font>

243
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I do? Hand wash it after all?</i></font>

244
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess it's finally back.</font>

245
00:15:01,290 --> 00:15:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyusho-kun...</font>

246
00:15:03,010 --> 00:15:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

247
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, but I have to 
get back to work right away!</font>

248
00:15:07,970 --> 00:15:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

249
00:15:09,300 --> 00:15:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel free to relax 
and make yourself at home.</font>

250
00:15:16,210 --> 00:15:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There she goes again.</font>

251
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#525155"><font size="30">Start</font></font></b></font>

252
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#525155"><font size="30">Pause</font></font></b></font>

253
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These go here...</font>

254
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and these here.</font>

255
00:16:27,250 --> 00:16:28,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Phew.</font>

256
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think we're done.</font>

257
00:16:32,760 --> 00:16:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

258
00:16:34,510 --> 00:16:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much for your help.</font>

259
00:16:36,900 --> 00:16:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing.</font>

260
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should be able to use the shower now,
 so why don't you go on in first?</font>

261
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'll give me a chance 
to get your futon ready.</font>

262
00:16:51,820 --> 00:16:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Thanks.</font>

263
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll have to check out 
the backyard tomorrow.</i></font>

264
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

265
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That tree went straight through 
the roof over the porch.</font>

266
00:17:21,710 --> 00:17:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'm out, so go ahead.</font>

267
00:17:25,570 --> 00:17:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinme-san?</font>

268
00:17:27,910 --> 00:17:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what?</font>

269
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyusho-kun...</font>

270
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

271
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, would you mind if we slept
 in the same room tonight?</font>

272
00:17:38,580 --> 00:17:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about the other room?</font>

273
00:17:40,530 --> 00:17:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, since I got to finish washing, 
I'm using it to dry clothes right now.</font>

274
00:17:46,540 --> 00:17:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really so sorry!</font>

275
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't want to, 
I can sleep in the hallway.</font>

276
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I can't... make you do that...</font>

277
00:17:56,510 --> 00:18:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I mean, if it doesn't 
bother you, I don't care.</font>

278
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

279
00:18:03,410 --> 00:18:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh boy.</i></font>

280
00:18:05,970 --> 00:18:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll go take a bath too.</font>

281
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:32,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Actually, last time I was in this room...</i></font>

282
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>was the day that happened.</i></font>

283
00:18:50,620 --> 00:18:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. Did I wake you?</font>

284
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's okay. I was still awake.</font>

285
00:19:08,090 --> 00:19:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, good night.</font>

286
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good night.</font>

287
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still some rumbling
 in the distance.</font>

288
00:19:26,830 --> 00:19:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like it.</font>

289
00:19:28,860 --> 00:19:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if it's that far away, 
I won't get scared, I think.</font>

290
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:39,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just now in the bath,</font>

291
00:19:39,710 --> 00:19:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I started wondering about what could 
have caused me to be so afraid of thunder.</font>

292
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:48,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what started it.</font>

293
00:19:54,420 --> 00:20:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I don't really know if 
I've ever been to Hatsushima before.</font>

294
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:08,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">The person I went with said it looked
 like I was lost in my memories there.</font></font>

295
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes even recent memories, 
memories from the last two years,</font>

296
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">just up and disappear on me.</font>

297
00:20:21,950 --> 00:20:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's almost like somebody who isn't me</font>

298
00:20:25,530 --> 00:20:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is doing things I'm not aware of 
when I'm not looking.</font>

299
00:20:30,940 --> 00:20:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't think there's anything 
I can do about that.</font>

300
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinme-san, if you ever forgot 
about me and Kuriru and Moruda,</font>

301
00:20:46,230 --> 00:20:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'd...</font>

302
00:21:32,380 --> 00:21:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you! I know this was asking a lot.</font>

303
00:21:35,520 --> 00:21:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it was fine! He even helped me out 
a bunch around the shop.</font>

304
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:43,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyu was helpful for once?</font>

305
00:21:43,530 --> 00:21:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, he sure was!</font>

306
00:21:45,930 --> 00:21:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyusho-kun, thank you for your help.</font>

307
00:21:53,170 --> 00:21:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well dang, Kyu! Nice job. Good for you!</font>

308
00:21:57,430 --> 00:21:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

309
00:21:58,420 --> 00:22:01,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyusho-kun! Your bag, your bag!</font>

310
00:22:10,770 --> 00:22:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#ba834a"><b>Translation:
Editing and Typesetting:</b></font></font></font></font>

